title: The Trouble with Larry
description: Petunia invents an imaginary friend to help her always get her way.

title: El Dia Divertido de Falafel
description: Cuando Falafel decide empacar sus cosas e ir a la ciudad, Manzana y Cebollín deben convencerlo de quedarse.

title: Guantes, Guantes Maestros
description: Los nuevos guantes de Owen hacen que sea muy hábil en todo. Pero su grandeza tiene un precio.

title: Not So Secret Service
description: After Mojo Jojo's latest creation threatens to blast him into tiny bits, the Powerpuff Girls are forced to take Mojo in.

title: Worship
description: When the Fashionistas unveil their new mind controlling perfume, the Powerpuff Girls must find a way to stop them before Townsville falls under their spell.

title: Shmorby
description: The Bears get a Shmorby home assistant device and become lazy couch potatoes.

title: Captain Bamboozle
description: Mr. Mxyzptlk decides to create some mischief by endowing Shazam's well-meaning Uncle Dudley with superpowers bigger than anyone in the league.

title: The Crew
description: When Gumball and Darwin decide it's time they join a crew, they agree that the coolest posse in Elmore is the Senior Citizens. They do everything they can to fit in with them, going to extraordinary lengths to prove themselves worthy of running (well, walking very slowly) with them.

title: Drawn to Sports with Hannah
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating young athletes from all over the country who are Drawn to Sports! Hannah competes in track and field.

title: Cuentos de miedo 2
description: Es Halloween de nuevo y la banda trata de contar aterradoras historias a un grupo de niños que piden dulces.

title: It Grows
description: As everyone celebrates Valentino for growing his first facial hair, a jealous Vic resorts to magical methods to grow a mustache and compete for attention.

title: Itch to Explore
description: Craig's quest to map the entire Creek takes him and his friends into the treacherous Poison Ivy Grove.

title: Cat Man Do/Impeach Fuzz
description: Cat Man Do: Bubbles saves a seemingly innocent kitty from the clutches of an evil villain. But when the girls discover it's actually the Cat who is evil, they must save the Professor from being the next victim./Impeach Fuzz: When Fuzzy Lumkins throws his hat into the mayoral ring and claims a surprise victory, it's up to the Mayor and the girls to wrestle the office, and the Mayor's actual hat, back from him.

title: Lie-Ranosaurus Wrecked
description: Owen pretends to be Izzy's pet dinosaur after leading her to believe she dug him up in the school playground.

title: Out to Launch
description: While on a visit to Cape Canaveral, the Tennyson Trio are present for the inaugural launch of an experimental space plane. When Vilgax commandeers the ship, Ben must stop the baddie from weaponizing the shuttle before the countdown hits zero.

title: Earthlings
description: Amethyst tries to exact revenge with a showdown in the Kindergarten.

title: Robo Teacher
description: When a substitute teacher fills in for Chef, Duncan thinks it's going to be the best day ever. He's wrong.

title: An UnbeLEAFable Day
description: While the trains are setting up for the Vicarstown Fall Festival, Thomas is feeling down about the end of summer and the changing weather.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: The Beepers: The Visitor
description: The Beepers find the perfect groove after a new friend shreds a little too hard.

title: Scary Tales 2
description: It's Halloween again and the gang is desperately trying to tell the scariest story to a couple of trick or treaters. Each of the characters takes turns adding onto the last story, going through a haunted glove to a haunted action figure to haunted everything, and even a spooky song! None work in scaring the kids when suddenly a full scale alien invasion happens right before their eyes! Still, the trick or treaters are unimpressed until Richard takes the story stage and delivers a story no kid wants to hear- instead of candy, the trick or treaters would get granola bars! The kids, and Puppycorn, run away screaming.

title: We Are Heroes
description: KO struggles with his upgraded role as a member of the hero team.

title: Magic Act
description: Pocoyo is doing a magic show. He expects everyone to watch very carefully and take him very seriously but unfortunately his tricks don't quite go to plan and his friends all laugh. They're really enjoying the show. They think Pocoyo is great at being a funny magician. But that's not what Pocoyo wants to be - he wants to be taken very seriously - so he goes off in a huff. In the meantime, Pato, Elly and Baby Bird go around Pocoyo-land to tell everyone about the magnificent hilarious magician whose show they enjoy so much. As Pocoyo sulks, his friends gather around him, excited to see his tricks. Pocoyo is overwhelmed that his friends liked his show so much. He does some more tricks and his friends are thrilled.

title: Wide Load Vacay: Dumbrella
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, have been traveling on the back of a truck in the rain for days. Charlie produces an umbrella to help his friend but unfortunately it's a "dumbrella" and it's looking to have some fun with them!

title: Melissa the Hero
description: Melissa brags about helping Petunia to the point of self-aggrandizement.

title: Winning at Whining
description: Vambre's challenge to Prohyas: Don't whine for the entirety of the next mission and you can have the Magisword we get at the end.

title: Ghost Princess
description: Finn and Jake try to solve Ghost Princess' unsolved murder.

title: Let's Meet Sonic
description: When world class hero SONIC THE HEDGEHOG visits the plaza, he teams up with KO to save the day.

title: Top of the Titans: Best Love Songs
description: The Titans follow their heart with songs devoted to their greatest relationships: Beast Boy & Raven, Cyborg & Jinx and the Titans & Food.

title: Sandcastle
description: The Baby Bears build a giant sandcastle. But when some kids declare war on the Bears, they must fight to defend their new home.

title: Fiesta en el Calabozo
description: Cole, Wu y la Princesa Vania conocen a un grupo de sobrevivientes llamados los de abajo, ellos cuentan cómo terminaron en "Lo más profundo".

title: Gryffindor v Hufflepuff
description: Dame Helen Mirren hosts the first episode of this epic TV event series. Over 4 episodes the Houses of Hogwarts will do battle to see which team knows the most about the wizarding world, featuring celebrity guests, actors from the original films and more Harry Potter Magic than you could find on a day trip to Diagon Alley. Tonight's match up sees the brave Gryffindors face the loyal Hufflepuffs for a guaranteed place in the grand finale.
originalseriesname: Harry Potter: Hogwarts Tournament of Houses

title: Crece
description: Mientras todo el mundo celebra a Valentino porque le creció su primer vello facial, Vic se pone celoso y recurre a métodos mágicos para dejarse crecer el bigote y competir por la atención.

title: Breakup
description:
Feeling left out, Adorabat wishes Mao Mao and Badgerclops would spend less time with each other and more time with her. When she gets
what she wishes for and accidentally breaks up their friendship, only the secret of their past can bring them back together.

title: Wiener Club
description: Puppycorn is determined to become the Hot Dog King and joins an underground hot dog eating contest called Weiner Club. Rick warns "you are what you eat," but Puppycorn doesn't listen and eats so many hot dogs he becomes the new champion of Weiner Club. Unfortunately he also literally turns into a hot dog, that the other club members reveal they are going to eat! Unikitty and the gang now must attack with vegetables and defeat the hot dog-eating baddies in order to save the giant hot-dog-shaped Puppycorn and turn him back to normal.

title: Clayton
description: Darwin needs to find a photo of Clayton to put on the cover of the school yearbook - but he makes the mistake of seeking help from Tobias, who has his eye on the cover spot himself! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Worm Bin
description: After his mom gets a worm bin, Jeff deals with the gross reality that he has a tub of bugs living in his kitchen, and Clarence obsesses over feeding the worms.

title: Tips
description: Apple and Onion have to find a way to ride the Hot Air Balloon which is in their town for one day only.

title: Queen of the Munce
description: Jay, Nya and Lloyd are led deep into the Mines of Shintaro by Murt, who brings them back to the Munce "Home- Cave" - a settlement deep in the mountain. There, complications arise when they meet the Munce Queen, Murtessa, who takes a liking to Jay.

title: Top of the Titans:  Raddest Songs
description: From "Booty Scooty" to "Sour Grapes" to "The Night Begins to Shine," Birdarang is here to count down the raddest music from Teen Titans Go!

title: Drawn to Change
description: Cartoon Network is Drawn to Change, and Craig of the Creek talks to Martin Luther King Junior's granddaughter Yolanda about how kids can change the world!

title: Buen Viaje
description: Abordo del SS Pettigrew en su último viaje, Ben debe luchar no solo contra el mareo sino también contra Vapor Smythe, que se propone usar a sus criaturas mecánicas para hundir el barco moderno que remplaza al vapor... iy a sus pasajeros!

title: Shrimps and Prime Rib
description: The Titans try to remember how to be superheroes in order to stop The Brain.

title: The Skull Sorcerer
description: Separated from the others, Cole must trust his instincts and make the right choices to find his way to the surface to alert King Vangelis of the dangerous Skull Sorcerer.

title: Ocean
description: Blippi's trusty BlippiMobile safely transports him to a whole new underwater world! He dives into the sea, where he gets an ocean tour from a local resident, Jerry the Jellyfish. They swim through a huge kelp forest, explore the ocean floor and meet interesting underwater creatures along the way!

title: Top of the Titans: Beast Boy & Cyborg Songs
description: Birdarang counts down the best musical moments from the raddest bros you know, Beast Boy and Cyborg. Waffles!

title: Weapon XI Part 2
description: The Rooters have seemingly turned Kevin and the Amalgam kids against Ben. Can Rook and Gwen help him overcome the opposition and escape the Null Void?

title: Despeguemos
description: De excursión en Cabo Cañaveral, el trío Tennyson presencia el lanzamiento inaugural de una nave espacial experimental, pero cuando Vilgax comanda la nave, Ben debe impedir que el villano use el transbordador como arma antes de que la cuenta regresiva llegue a cero.

title: Suitable Armor
description: A veteran warrior insists that Vambre is under dressed for battle and takes it upon herself to garb Vambre in armor as Prohyas fights the beast solo without armor.

title: Separacion
description: Adorabat siente que es dejada de lado y desea que Mao Mao y Colosal pasen menos tiempo juntos y más tiempo con ella. Pero cuando el deseo de Adorabat se hace realidad y destruye la amistad de Mao Mao y Colosal, solo el secreto de su pasado podrá volver a unirlos.

title: Ganas de Explorar
description: La misión de Craig de mapear el Arroyo entero los lleva a él y a sus amigos a arboleda traicionera de Hiedra Venenosa
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Fire!
description: Grizz's quick thinking prevents a potential wild fire, but the praise he receives from doing so quickly goes to his head.

title: Lego DC Super Hero Girls: Brain Drain
description: Missing memories provide an intriguing mystery for everyone's favorite young female heroes in this all-new animated film.  When Supergirl, Wonder Woman, Batgirl, Harley Quinn, Bumblebee, Poison Ivy and Katana suddenly realize they cannot remember a single moment from their Monday at Super Hero High, the young Super Heroes spring into sleuthing action! Suspecting foul-play, they band together to retrace their steps and uncover the mystery of who exactly stole their memories - and, what nefarious plan might be afoot?

title: Duo Espinoso
description: Después de dejar Pequeña Escuela Madre, Steven ha encontrado un nuevo pasatiempo: las plantas.

title: Drawn to Sports with Luke
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating young athletes from all over the country who are Drawn to Sports! Luke is passionate about running, jumping and climbing in Ninja Racing.

title: Mayhem in Mascot
description: After their attempt to get a photo with every storefront mascot is foiled, Ben and Gwen sneak out at night to get their photo with the wooden bear totem known as "Yawk", only to find he and the other mascots have come to life!

title: Cool for Cats
description: Sylvester believes a commercial that says eating Chewy Chomps will make him cool.

title: Glove Glove Me Do
description: Owen's newly found gloves make him great at everything. But this greatness comes at a high price.

title: Sarah
description: Darwin asks Sarah for a photo to put on the cover of the school yearbook. But when Sarah tries to help, things get a little sticky. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Top of the Titans: Dance Party!
description: Come correct because it's a Titans Dance Battle! Birdarang reviews the greatest dance songs in Teen Titans Go! history.

title: Permanent Retirement
description: Grandpa, Gwen and Ben visit an old maid relative only to find that her retirement community has been overtaken by a shapeshifting aliens called Limax.

title: Boss For a Day
description: When Chata lets Vic be the boss of the taco stand for the day Vic decides to fire Val, which has disastrous consequences.

title: Wide Load Vacay: Big City Dancers
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, traveling on the back of a truck visit NYC where the rhythms of the city make Charlie wanna dance his little back porch off. Frank … not so much. But when you go far enough into the city, anything can happen.

title: Teachers
description: When Darwin asks his friends which teacher deserves to be on the yearbook cover, they struggle to find a single worthy candidate! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: El Hechicero Calavera
description: Separado de los demás, Cole debe encontrar su camino a la superficie para advertir al Rey Vangelis sobre el peligroso Hechicero Calavera.

title: Drawn To Expression!
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating queer youth and families in the LGBTQIA+ community that radiate joy, pride, and inclusivity. We are championing the ways these kids and families form connections to their authentic selves by expressing their creativity and queer identity through their art.

title: The Tooth About Zombies
description: When Gwen's favorite event, the Zombie March, falls on the same day as Noah's nightmare event, dental hygienist check up day, Gwen and Noah find a way to help each other out.

title: Tree of Life
description: Clarence, Jeff and Sumo make it their mission to climb a really tall tree before it's set to be chopped down. As they scale higher and higher their reality begins to slip away.

title: We Baby Bears: BHA Bha Song
description: We Baby Bears follows baby bear brothers Grizz, Panda, and Ice Bear as they journey in a magical box to fantastic different worlds in search of their perfect home.

title: Little Graduation
description: Steven and the Gems celebrate Little Homeschool's first graduating class.

title: Too Hot to Handle/The Big Squeak/Big Jumping Spider
description: Findley can't resist some freshly baked cookies that are too hot to eat./ Avocado's new toy is driving everyone crazy with its noisy squeaker./ Lucas performs epic jumps all around House./ Findley is nervous and wishes Lucas wouldn't jump.

title: Alan
description: Darwin wants to put Alan on the cover of the school yearbook - but Alan's apparent modesty gets in the way. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: No Honor Among Bros
description: Rook is under the influence of Fistrick's "bro" essence, and starts to act like a bro. Can he and Ben infiltrate an alien fight club to claim the Golden Fist? (Introducing Slix Vigma, alien promoter.)

title: Just Another Manic Mojo/Mime for a Change
description: Just Another Manic Mojo: The Powerpuff Girls lose their baseball in Mojo's house, offering him the perfect opportunity to destroy these pesky superheroines if he can only get them to sit still./Mime for a Change: An accidental bleach spill turns Rainbow the Clown into the malevolent Mr. Mime. He proceeds to turn Townsville black and white and dead all over.

title: The Origins Part 2
description: Via the sewers, Darwin finds himself flushed out to sea. He is terrified but determined to make his way back to the Wattersons. However, a fish can't get very far on land so Darwin will have to do millions of years of evolution in a matter of hours if he's going to get home safe and sound.

title: El Libro Final
description: El último libro de fantasía de la serie favorita de Kelsey desaparece de la biblioteca. Por eso, Craig decide ayudarla a resolver el misterio de quién se lo llevó.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Ranger Norm
description: When Tabes leaves for a conference, the Bears have to deal with her substitute, Ranger Norm.

title: Bubblevicious/The Bare Facts
description: Bubblevicious: Bubbles is tired of people dismissing her as more sugar than spice. When she sets out to prove she's hardcore, she takes everyone by surprise, even Mojo Jojo./The Bare Facts: After Mojo kidnaps and blindfolds him, the Mayor has to rely on the girls' very different individual accounts of the crime to figure out exactly what happened.

title: Apple's in Trouble
description: Apple is challenged to a fight by a grumpy Cheesesteak, so he and Onion go on a quest to find the source of Cheesesteak's grumpiness.

title: Trouble Busters!/French Fry Wars
description: Trouble Busters!: Now that the Awesome Brawlers are world famous Bakugan experts, they want to help people solve their Bakugan-related problems. When the world's quietest town is experiencing unexplained noises, the Awseome Brawlers are called in to get to the bottom of it./French Fry Wars: The Awesome Brawlers are arguing over who gets to eat the last french-fry. At first, each member makes a case for why they should to be the one to eat it. But the quarrel quickly escalates into trash talk and revealing secrets about one another. With everyone now upset, things take an unexpected turn.

title: Old Lady Bodyguard
description: After being "bought" at a charity auction, Hawkodile is forced to spend the day as Old Lady Edith's personal bodyguard.

title: Accidents Happen Boo Boo Song
description: Ella falls over, but Heidi the Horse teaches her to get right back up again!

title: El Club Salchicha
description: Perricornio está decidido a convertirse en el rey de los hot dogs y se une al Club Salchicha, una competencia clandestina de comer hot dogs.

title: Diente de Zombi
description: Cuando el evento favorito de Gwen, el Desfile de los Zombies, cae el mismo día que el día de pesadilla de Beth, la revisión con el dentista, las dos chicas encuentran un modo de ayudarse entre sí.

title: Back to the Moon
description: Steven and the Gems revisit the Moon Base.

title: The Beepers: Funky Time
description: The Beepers play with tempo and learn that adapting to change can be…sweaty.

title: Enemy Mime
description: When the Sheriff's Dept fights a monster that copies their every move, they'll have to find a way to fight without fighting.

title: The Sale
description: Gumball and Darwin are devastated to learn that Mr. Robinson, their favorite person in the world, is selling his house and leaving town. When they realize that making some final happy memories with Mr. Robinson is not enough for them, they decide to stop him leaving by sabotaging the sale.

title: Holly Jolly Secrets Part 1
description: Finn and Jake continue to explore the world of old Christmas specials while the Ice King fumes.

title: Eggy Head
description: Bing and his friends are at Amma's creche today making Eggy Heads! Amma explains that Eggy Heads need 7 sleeps, water, light and patience to grow it's cress hair. But Bing has an idea to help his Eggy grow cress hair quicker...

title: We Baby Bears Official Trailer: New Series
description: These baby bears are searching for a brand new home, and they're off to fantastical worlds and new adventures along the way. Watch the official trailer for We Baby Bears, the brand new show from the creators of We Bare Bears, coming to Cartoon Network in 2022.

title: Getting Truffy with It
description: Truff is happy. He has found a necklace that makes him even Truffier! Except he had no idea the necklace belongs to Starmush. And the Mushelder promised there will be consequences for whoever took it. Mush-Mush, Chep and Lilit now have to save Truff from being consequenced.

title: Firework Run
description: Mordecai, Rigby and Muscle Man have to get fireworks for an event at the park because they used the ones Benson got.

title: Alpha Bodies
description: Cartoonito presents Alpha Bodies! It's time to use our bodies to make every letter of the alphabet, from A to Z, but one over-eager letter keeps getting ahead of itself.

title: Collection Infection
description: Having pared down their Magisword collection, the Warriors are forced into unconventional battle choices on a dangerous mission into the Deepest Darkest Woods.

title: Banana Joe
description: When Principal Brown sets Darwin the task of making the school yearbook, Darwin starts by asking class clown Banana Joe for a simple selfie to put on the cover. But with Banana Joe, things are never that simple. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Dark Plaza
description: KO and the heroes of the Plaza fight to save Lakewood Plaza Turbo with everything on the line.

title: Drawn to Sports with Olivia
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating young athletes from all over the country who are Drawn to Sports! Olivia is a tennis player who is also passionate about art.

title: Special Delivery
description: After being rudely interrupted by Bim Bom during her daily morning song, an angry Unikitty takes the advice of her friends and writes down her feelings into a letter with the intention of keeping the letter to herself, but then accidentally sends it off, complete with postage! The gang then goes on a wild chase through the Unikingdom mail delivery service to keep that rude letter from getting into the hands of Bim Bom, and ultimately hurting her feelings. Turns out, Unikitty's "rude" is everyone else's "nice" and the letter was full of compliments.

title: La Reina de los Munces
description: Jay, Nya y Lloyd son guiados entre las minas de Shintaro por Murt, quien los lleva de vuelta a la Cueva de los Munces. A la Reina Munce le gusta Jay.

title: DC Super Hero Girls: Super Hero High
description: Supergirl arrives at Super Hero High and struggles to learn to control her new powers. Meanwhile, the Junior Detective Club investigates a mysterious rash of security breaches centered around the teleportation Boom Tubes.

title: Jessica Goes to the Creek
description: When Craig and Jessica are locked out of the house, Craig has no choice but to bring his little sister to the Creek.

title: The Real Fall!
description: An entire episode chronicles the ninja's most bizarre adventure yet: in which Cole, Princess Vania and Master Wu fall down a seemingly endless tunnel, into the bowels of Shintaro Mountain.

title: Lightning Bark
description: Fung and Miff have come across a rare piece of bark struck by lightning. Chep desperately wants to add it to his collection, but Fung and Miff have no intention to give it to him. Now remembering every time Chep has been nice to them, Fung and Miff end up doing something they never thought possible…

title: Juicio de Mino
description: Un grupo de Geckles creen que Kai y Zane están aliados con el Hechicero Calavera y los llevan con su líder, quien los somete a un juicio por Mino…

title: The Phantom Thief Comes to Call/Phantom Thief Ajit
description: The Phantom Thief Comes to Call: An archeological discovery is made in Los Volmos. Exploration at the site is cut short, when a master thief and his apprentice attempt to steal the ancient Bakugan artifacts. When the Awesome Brawlers hear the news, they step in to thwart the thieves./Phantom Thief Ajit: An Ancient Bakugon artifact from an archeological discovery is placed in the Los Volmos Museum. The Awesome Brawlers are charged with guarding the artifacts from any further attempts thievery.

title: Universe vs. Tennyson
description: Ben gets dragged into intergalactic court by the other Celestialsapiens (Alien Xs) for recreating the universe (back in "So Long and Thanks for All the Smoothies").

title: Splash Zone
description: Mayor Foghorn Leghorn hires The Looney Builders to build a giant water slide for Looneyburg's waterpark. He keeps adding onto the design with the support of Bugs until problems arise.

title: You're It
description: A vicious game of tag wreaks havoc on the Creek, claiming Kelsey as the next it.

title: Agua de Pescado
description: Starfire gana un pececito en el carnaval y jura que lo mantendrá con vida.

title: Entrega especial
description: Después de ser interrumpida por Bim Bom durante su canción matutina, una furiosa Unikitty sigue el consejo de sus amigos y escribe sus sentimientos en una carta con la intención de quedársela, pero la envía accidentalmente. La banda sale en una salvaje persecución de los servicios postales del Unireino para evitar que la irrespetuosa carta llegue a Bim Bom y hiera sus sentimientos.

title: Los Cadejos
description: Val le guarda rencor a Vic, lo cual atrae sin querer a un malvado cadejo, una bestia mitológica parecida a un lobo.

title: La Traes
description: Un despiadado juego de persecución desata un caos en el Arroyo, y se declara a Kelsey como la próxima perseguidora.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: T.G.I. Tuesday
description: Mordecai, Rigby and Eileen want to celebrate Margaret's new internship before she has to quit the coffee shop.

title: Batalla en El Biggie Box
description: Ben y Billy Billions se enfrentan por un set de sumo exclusivo que se vende únicamente en el centro comercial más grande del mundo, isolo para descubrir que Simon Sez, de apenas seis años, lo compró primero! Así se desata una batalla dentro de una tienda que parece tenerlo todo excepto una salida fácil de encontrar.

title: #CrashCourse
description: When a high-speed chase breaks out during her driver's test, Diana Prince's desire to fight evil clashes with her desire to undergo a World of Man teenage rite of passage, getting her license.

title: No Me Impresiona
description: Cuando un Corazoncito no se siente impresionado con las hazañas del departamento del sheriff, nuestros tres héroes intentan de todo para conquistarlo.

title: El Grupo
description: Gumball y Darwin intentan unirse a la pandilla de los más malos de la ciudad.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: The Rowdy Ruff Boys
description: Mojo Jojo creates the ultimate weapons against the Powerpuff Girls, boy equivalents! Enter Butch, Boomer and Brick, The Rowdyruff Boys.

title: Hello Around the World
description: Cartoonito presents Hello Around the World! All across the globe, friends greet each other in lots of different languages. Watch along and discover some of the many ways to say "Hello," around the world and beyond!

title: Superado
description: Cuando Rufus y Reg llegan para engañar al pueblo, el sheriff Mao Mao les enseña una lección sobre la justicia.

title: Garage Sale
description: Robin makes the other Titans sell their treasured mementos from past episodes.

title: Manzana esta en Problemas
description: Bistec con Queso, malhumorado, desafía a Manzana a una pelea. De ese modo, Manzana puede embarcarse con Cebollín en una misión para encontrar el origen del malhumor de Bistec con Queso.

title: A New Life
description: Apple and Onion both leave their homes and follow their dreams to the big city but things don't go quite to plan.

title: Demasiados Tesoros
description: Con la esperanza de reparar su fuerte, Craig consigue la ayuda de Los Veloces Diez para llevarlos hasta la legendaria pila de basura.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Excalibear
description: On the Bears' visit to a medieval vegetable-village, Grizz starts to believe that he's the rightful king.

title: Some Luck
description: While the Bears are transporting a Whiffle Wizard to a distant meadow, Good Luck seems to have a run of bad luck. His belief in his own bad fortune causes him to lose confidence, causing ever more "bad luck." It's only when he understands that we make our own luck that his "luck" changes.

title: Tourist Trap
description: While messing with the World's Largest Rubberband Ball at a tourist trap, Ben accidently releases some mischievous electrical creatures.

title: The Beepers: Spotlight
description: When a spotlight gives everyone a chance to solo, a shy Beeper discovers the courage to shine.

title: Atrapagritos
description: Cuando una caries obliga a Ben a ir al dentista, su día empeora aún más cuando el malévolo mago Hex usa un atrapasueños para materializar los miedos de nuestro héroe y los transporta con él a un lugar pesadillesco.

title: Drawn To Rhythm: Lorenzo
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Hispanic Heritage Month with another installment of "Drawn To" that showcases kids who honor their Hispanic and Latino heritage as they are drawn to rhythm. In this piece, Lorenzo tells us about his passion for reggaetón music and soccer.

title: Bath Song
description: Ella gets covered in mud so she goes into Mei's farmhouse to have a bath.

title: The Perfect Team
description: Onion worries his relationship with Apple is in jeopardy when a stray cat enters the picture.

title: Fish Water
description: Starfire wins a goldfish at the carnival and vows to keep it alive.

title: Drawn To Juneteenth: Julian
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Juneteenth! Juneteenth commemorates the end of slavery with celebrations that take place every year on June 19th! This holiday recognizes the day that all slaves were free in the U.S.! We are recognizing those who are dedicated to making this special holiday known as they are Drawn to...Juneteenth!

title: Pocoyo's Puppet Show
description: Pocoyo finds a puppet theatre and some puppets. Brilliant! Time for him to be a puppeteer. He puts on a show for Caterpillar and Baby Bird. They love it, especially when the puppets do funny things like fall over. They bring Pato and Elly along to watch the show too. When Pocoyo makes fun of Pato and Elly with the puppets, Pato and Elly are nonplussed. They don't think it's so great to laugh at people. Pocoyo realizes that his show has upset his friends. He says sorry and explains he didn't mean it. Everyone makes friends again!

title: Victor y la Lechuza
description: Después de fingir una lesión para no tener que trabajar, Vic se gana la compasión de todos mientras que, sin saberlo, atrae la atención de una peligrosa criatura mítica.

title: TKO Rules!
description: KO and TKO decide to swap places for the day.

title: #FantasticBeastsAndHowToMindThem
description: Diana Prince receives a care package from home, and her pet-raising skills are soon put to the test when a mysterious egg hatches into a baby griffin.

title: Bon Voyage
description: Aboard the SS Pettigrew on its final voyage, Ben must not only battle seasickness but Steam Smythe, who looks to use his mechanical creatures to sink the steamship's modern replacement and the passengers with it!

title: Hunted
description: Three alien bounty hunters are hot on Ben's trail. But one of them is a secret agent trying to make sure the Omnitrix does not fall into evil hands.

title: Modern-ish Stone Age Family
description: The Bears are invited to live with a family of cavemen but things get rocky when the bears teach the family about television.

title: Dungeon Party
description: Having survived their fall into the mountain, Cole, Wu and Princess Vania befriend a motley group of survivors, called the Lowly, and are told the story of how they too ended up at "Rock-Bottom."

title: In Bugs We Trust
description: Bugs uses the babies' money to buy different toys than he promised.

title: Another Way
description: The tears of a crying Cyclops just might heal Finn and Jake's broken toes.

title: Weapon XI Part 1
description: Kevin and Argit attempt to warn the amalgam kids about the Rooters intentions meanwhile Ben, Rook, and Gwen set off to find Kevin and land themselves in the Null Void!

title: Lunch
description: Bing and Sula are chefs today and helping Amma and Flop make lunch. It's Sula's favourite - Easy Peasy Pasta! But, what happens when lunch is served and Bing sees all the ingredients mixed up together?

title: Honey
description: Blippi and FETCH shrink down and fly inside a very active beehive, where they meet Bijon, the fast-talking, fast-moving Worker Bee. With a talent for rhyming and making honey, Bijon rhymes her way through the sweet explanation of how delicious honey is made. What a very buzzy... erm...busy day!

title: Beta
description: Steven and Amethyst visit some friends in the country but Amethyst isn't being herself.

title: Birthday
description: Jeff and Sumo expect no one to show at Clarence's birthday party, just like last year. When dozens of kids arrive, the boys struggle to get face time with Clarence, the popular party host.

title: Enemigo Mimo
description: Cuando el departamento del sheriff se enfrenta a un monstruo que copia todos los movimientos, tendrán que encontrar el modo de pelear sin pelear.

title: Blossom3
description: After being blasted by Duplikate, Blossom turns into a triple threat.

title: The Parking
description: When the Wattersons arrive at the mall for a day of shopping, they struggle to find a space in the parking lot. They search for a space everywhere using all their intelligence, cunning and trickery but as the day goes on, the desperate hunt for a space becomes more important than the trip to the mall itself.

title: Baku-Gear/Bakugan Rock!
description: Baku-Gear: The Awesome Brawlers are excited over their discovery of Baku-Gear, and want to get some footage of it in action. While they're filming, an underclassman named Trey challenges Dan to battle. Who will emerge victorious in the impromptu battle?/Bakugan Rock!: Baku-gear has shown up twice for Dan and Drago and it's starting to eat away at the other awesome brawlers. It's time they take it into their own hands. When Lia and Wynton go up against the rockin' new brawlers in town, they show Dan and Drago that they are not the only one who can summon this cool new tool!

title: Desastre en Mascota
description: Frustrado su intento de conseguir una foto con cada mascota de vidriera, Ben y Gwen se escabullen de noche para tomarse su foto con el tótem del oso de madera... iy descubren que él y las demás mascotas cobraron vida!

title: I See You
description: Robin brings Starfire on a fake stakeout in an attempt to get a kiss, while Cyborg and Beast Boy hold their own stakeout to discover Raven's dark secret.

title: Drawn to Ancestry
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Asian-American Pacific Islander Heritage Month and recognizing amazing kids who learn from their elders to pave their future! We're honoring the special bond between kids and their grandparents as they are Drawn To Ancestry.

title: Outfoxed
description: When Rufus and Reg come to swindle the town, Sheriff Mao Mao teaches them a lesson in justice.

title: Drawn To Juneteenth: Ms. Opal
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Juneteenth! Juneteenth commemorates the end of slavery with celebrations that take place every year on June 19th! This holiday recognizes the day that all slaves were free in the U.S.! We are recognizing those who are dedicated to making this special holiday known as they are Drawn to...Juneteenth!

title: Screamcatcher
description: When a cavity forces Ben to the dentist his day gets even worse when the malevolent magician Hex uses a nearby dream catcher to bring our hero's fears to life and transports them both to a nightmarish dreamscape.

title: Agua de Ensalada Caliente
description: Robin debe salvar a los Estados Unidos de una nueva invasión británica cuando beber té vuelve ingleses a los demás Titanes.

title: Not Impressed
description: When a Sweetypie isn't impressed with the sheriff dept's antics, our three heroes try everything to win him over.

title: Keeping Up with the Kryptonians
description: Mr. Mxyzptlk shows Supergirl and Superman that their innate goodness might not be so pure when he takes them to a parallel world where their counterparts are impossibly aggressive and spoiled.

title: Jefe por un dia
description: Cuando Chata deja que Vic sea el jefe del puesto de tacos por un día, él decide despedir a Val, lo que trae consecuencias desastrosas.

title: Snake Babies
description: Charlie adopts baby snakes despite the Bears thinking he's not ready for parenthood.

title: Too Many Treasures
description: Hoping to fix their fort, Craig enlists the 10 Speeds to give them a ride to the legendary Junk Pile.

title: #ItsComplicated
description: When Hal Jordan sees Carol Ferris with a new boyfriend, his ego can't handle the rejection, resulting in the most absurd Lantern battle ever.

title: Wide Load Vacay: Eye Spy
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, are traveling on the back of a truck from Montana to Utah. Charlie wants to play a game of Eye Spy. He finds more and more obvious objects for Frank to spy but Frank isn't quite getting the hang of it. Yet!

title: Drawn To Rhythm: Jayleen
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Hispanic Heritage Month with another installment of "Drawn To" that showcases kids who honor their Hispanic and Latino heritage as they are drawn to rhythm. In this piece, Jayleen shows us some of the eight different dance styles she can do, including bachata and cumbia.

title: Ghost Camp/Boo/Never Boop a Robot
description: When Lucas and friends go camping, Avocado tells a scary story. Lucas now thinks there's a ghost in the garden./ Lucas loves to give his friends a scare on Halloween./ When Lucas boops a robot, he and his friends are chased around House!

title: El Menti-Ranosaurio
description: Owen finge ser el dinosaurio mascota de Izzy después de hacerle creer que lo sacó del patio de la escuela.

title: Mine
description: Bing and Pando are on their way home from the beach! And when Pando goes back to Bing's house to collect Bullabaloo, they decide to play one last game before bedtime - Hide and Seek. But where will Pando hide?

title: El Equipo Perfecto
description: A Cebollín le preocupa que su relación con Manzana corra peligro cuando un gato callejero entra en su vida.

title: Pequena graduacion
description: Steven y las Gemas celebran la primera clase de graduados de la Escuela Madre.

title: Marceline's Closet
description: Finn and Jake spend a nerve-wracking afternoon trapped in Marceline's closet.

title: Drawn To Juneteenth: Miss Juneteenth
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Juneteenth! Juneteenth commemorates the end of slavery with celebrations that take place every year on June 19th! This holiday recognizes the day that all slaves were free in the U.S.! We are recognizing those who are dedicated to making this special holiday known as they are Drawn to...Juneteenth!

title: In the Clouds
description: Uncle Grandpa helps a boy get his head out of the clouds and focused on his history test.

title: The Lepre-Con
description: On a St. Patrick's Day trip to Ireland, Uncle Grandpa and the gang cross paths with a sneaky leprechaun.

title: The Need for Feed/The Zipline Sisters of Treetop Woods
description: MacBarm is bringing food to his hungry chickens, that is, until all of the food falls out of his truck./Grandma and her twin sister want to recreate their old zipline act, but quickly discover that the zipline no longer exists!

title: Clarence and Sumo's Rexcellent Adventure
description: On a school trip to the Aberdale Natural History Museum, Clarence and Sumo check out the displays, goof around with the exhibits and even remove a tooth from the T-Rex display.

title: Bucky and the Howl
description: After Clarence learns Sumo's in the school musical, he joins up and enthusiastically promotes the show. On opening night with a packed house, stage fright takes hold of Sumo and he runs off leaving Clarence to go on alone.

title: Propinas
description: Luego de destruir por accidente el boleto de Falafel para un concierto, Manzana y Cebollín deben descubrir un modo de evitar la furia de Falafel.

title: The Littlest Tweety
description: Tweety is tired of being overlooked because of his diminutive size.

title: Robo-Maestra
description: Cuando una maestra suplente reemplaza a Chef, Duncan cree que será el mejor día de la historia. Se equivoca.

title: Blukic and Driba Go to Area 51
description: A mysterious Galvan arrives and demands Blukic and Driba to give back a super powerful weapon needed to stop a threat to Earth.

title: La Venganza de Bao Bao
description: Cuando el antiguo compañero de Mao Mao amenaza al reino, los amigos de Mao Mao tendrán que conocer su pasado para proteger el presente.

title: She Wore Red Velvet
description: When Booster and the JLA come under attack by a mysterious and unrelenting new villainess known as Red Velvet, Booster comes to realize she's actually the fiance he left at the altar in the future.

title: Carrie
description: Darwin sets out to find a photo of Carrie for the cover of the school yearbook - but they end up reminiscing about all their past spooky shenanigans. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Camarones y Costillas
description: Los Titanes intentan recordar cómo ser superhéroes para detener a Cerebro.

title: La Gran Caida
description: Este episodio relata cómo Cole, la princesa Vania y el maestro Wu caen por un túnel aparentemente interminable, dentro de la montaña de Shintaro.

title: Prickly Pair
description: After leaving Little Homeschool, Steven has found a new hobby, plants.

title: Los Cadejos
description: Val holds a grudge against Vic, unwittingly attracting an evil cadejo, a mythological wolf-like beast.

title: Brawler Headhunting/Lightning's Entrance Exam
description: Brawler Headhunting: As acting president of Kazami International, Shun is called upon to entertain another new young CEO Luca Schmidt, who's interested in doing business with the Kazami International. But Shun quickly realizes something is up when Luca tries woo him over to his brawling team - the Glanz Five. /Lightning's Entrance Exam: The Awesome Brawlers may be world famous heroes, but that doesn't mean they get out of going to school. They are still regular kids, doing regular kid things. But teachers may have something to say when Lightening decides he wants to join his buddies in the classroom.

title: Mojo the Great
description: In an effort to make himself great, Mojo steals the powers that makes the each of the Powerpuff girls the heroes they are.

title: The Mysterious Boy/A New Power
description: The Mysterious Boy: After stopping Tiko's rampage, the Awesome Brawlers have become world-famous heroes and Bakugan-mania sweeps the globe. With the Bakugan boom, brawling has been reinvented as a sporting game. In celebration of the Awesome Brawlers efforts, a tournament is being held in their honor. But the battles are quickly cut short when a rogue brawler and his golden Bakugan crash the event./A New Power: A Rogue brawler, Agit and his golden Bakugan have crashed the Awesome Brawlers party. Who is this brawler? How can he control a Golden Bakugan? Only one way to find out - Bakugan Brawl! Dan and Drago go head to head with the outsides to get to the bottom of it. Outmatched by their opponent, Dan and Drago get a little help from a new powerful weapon - Baku-Gear.

title: Picnic Puzzle
description: Pocoyo and Elly have organized a picnic and they leave Pato in charge of guarding the sandwiches while they get everything ready. Incredibly the sandwiches suddenly start moving around. Pato can't believe his eyes. When Pocoyo and Elly return they are angry with Pato. They think he took the sandwiches himself. They give him one more chance, leaving him in charge of guarding the cake. Once again, amazingly, the cake runs away apparently on its own. Pato is once again berated by Pocoyo and Elly until they see what's going on with their own eyes. Pocoyo investigates further and discovers who it is that's moving the food around: ANTS! Having worked out what's going on, the friends invite the ants along to the picnic and they all have fun together.

title: Unleashed
description: While the Justice League is away on a mission, Plastic Man is not only left in charge of the Watchtower, but also Superman's dog, Krypto.

title: Top of the Titans: Best Rivals
description: From Trigon to Terra to Darkseid, Robin counts down the worst of the worst: the greatest villains to ever challenge the Teen Titans!

title: Baby Bird Sitting
description: When Sleepy Bird has to pop out for a while, she needs someone to look after little Baby Bird. Pato volunteers because he thinks that's going to be a much easier job than tidying up the mess he's made with Pocoyo. Baby Bird, and his chum Caterpillar, run rings round Pato who eventually appeals to Pocoyo for help. Pocoyo thinks he can take care of the situation easily himself, but he similarly is foxed by the little tykes. Finally Pocoyo and Pato work out that in order to get the little ones to do what they want, they are going to need to collaborate. By the time Sleepy Bird returns, Baby Bird and Caterpillar are fast asleep. Little does Sleepy Bird know the chaos that got them to that point!

title: Trapped in the Tower
description: During a fun fireworks show, Unikitty and Master Frown become trapped in the horn of the Unikitty Castle when she catches Master Frown messing with her fireworks. Unikitty takes this as an opportunity to figure out why Master Frown is always such a Cranky McCrabby Face all the time, if only Master Frown would let his emotional guard down! She tries all kinds of tactics, a song, a dance, even a firework with a face drawn on it named "Professor Pow Pow, licensed therapist" Getting nowhere, Unikitty ends up raging out and setting the tower and all the fireworks alight. In desperation to not burn alive, Master Frown tells Unikitty a story about a younger Master Frown who was gifted a special lollipop but after a freak chain of events, was broken right before his eyes. Unikitty cries her eyes out and puts out the fires and then reveals it was her plan all along to get Master Frown to talk about his feelings!

title: KO, Rad, and Enid!
description: When confronted with their lack of a team gimmick, KO, Rad, and Enid wonder what their group identity should be.

title: Senior Sinisters
description: Harold concocts an anti-aging cream for Chef but when it turns the kids old Chef hides the reversal cream because taking care of old people is making him young again!

title: The Wicked
description: Gumball and Darwin try to find a single nice quality about their neighbor, Mrs Robinson.

title: #TheBirdAndTheBee
description: Meek little Karen Beecher is intimidated by big broody Carter Hall - both as a hero and a teen - until she discovers Hawkman's tragically romantic destiny and vows to use her vast knowledge of cheesy teen movies to help him reunite with his beloved.

title: Woof
description: Bing and Flop are in the park, when a doggie called Sunshine comes to play catch with them! Bing loves playing with Sunshine, but what will happen when Bing realises he can't keep Sunshine?

title: The Final Book
description: The last book of Kelsey's favorite fantasy series goes missing from the library, so Craig decides to help her solve the mystery of who took it.

title: DC Super Hero Girls: Intergalactic Games
description: Super Hero High is facing off against Korugar Academy in the Intergalactic Games, but Lena Luthor takes advantage of the gathering of supers to enact her villainous plan.

title: Trouble Clef
description: When Morbucks realizes that The Powerpuff Girls see her as a villain and not a friend, she sets out to turn the town against them.

title: #HousePest
description: When the Super Hero Girls discover that Diana doesn't actually have a home, they gladly open theirs up to her… until they discover that life with an Amazon is much more challenging than they expected.

title: Battle at Biggie Box
description: Ben and Billy Billions go head to head over a Sumo Slammer Set sold exclusively inside the world's largest shopping center, only to find six-year-old Simon Sez has gotten it first! A battle royal ensues inside a store that seemingly has everything except an easy to find exit.

title: Bubbled
description: Steven gets marooned in his bubble.

title: For the Love of Narwhal
description: Vambre rejects Darlin' Narwhal Magisword as being unfit for battle, but when Prohyas trains and brings out its full potential, Vambre resorts to improper extremes to get it back.

title: Valley of the Shamrocks
description: When Grumpy replaces mission navigator Good Luck with a computerized navigational gadget, Good Luck feels useless -- until he saves the Valley of the Shamrocks and is proclaimed a hero by the Whiffles, who don't want him to leave. He is torn between staying with the Whiffles and remaining with the Bears.

title: Falafel's Fun Day
description: When Falafel decides to pack up and leave the city, Apple and Onion have to convince him to stay or they'll have to leave too.

title: Everyone's Present
description: Wow… Presents! One for Pocoyo, one for Elly and one for Pato! How exciting. Pocoyo's present is some string, Pato gets some paper and Elly some sticks. They have fun for a while, each playing with their own present in a bid to prove that it's the best of the bunch. But ultimately the friends get a little bored with their respective gifts. After all, there's only so much you can do with one thing. In a huff, the friends throw their new toys on the floor. And this is when they see the potential of the presents: they can combine them. They put the presents together to make a kite. Wonderful, something they can all play with together.

title: The Longest Weekend
description: Muscle Man has to make it through a week without contacting Starla.

title: Trial By Mino
description: Separated from the others, Kai and Zane discover a party of Geckles who suspect them of being in league with the Skull Sorcerer, and bring them before their leader, Chancellor Gulch, who subjects them to a "Trial-By-Mino."

title: Jake vs. Me-Mow
description: Finn and Jake grapple with a tiny feline assassin.

title: Hot Salad Water
description: When drinking tea turns the other Titans English, it's up to Robin to save America from another British invasion.

title: Barehanded
description: When Green Lantern leaves his ring in an intergalactic restroom after washing his hands, he discovers it's gone, leading him on a wild chase for the aliens who might have taken it.

title: Atrapados en la torre
description: Durante un divertido espectáculo de fuegos artificiales, Unikitty y Master Frown quedan atrapados en el cuerno del castillo luego de que ella lo sorprende tratando de arruinar sus fuegos artificiales.

title: Jessica va al Arroyo
description: Cuando Craig y Jessica quedan encerrados fuera de la casa, Craig no tiene otra opción: debe llevar a su hermanita al Arroyo.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Bismuth
description: Steven discovers something the Gems thought was lost to the past inside of Lion's mane.

title: Ace Balthazar Lives
description: Mordecai and Rigby want to reunite the lead guitarist of Adrenaline with his band.

title: Cuddle Monster
description: After being told by Chata that they can't get a pet, Vic & Val adopt a wild lizard, unaware of its magical properties, and decide to keep it secret from Chata.

title: Sandwich of Death
description: Mordecai and Rigby have to find a cure for the Death Sandwich before Benson dies.

title: Wednesday - Part 2
description: Elliott and his mom Frankie are about to have a Wednesday they'll never forget, when a mysterious rock unexpectedly transports them somewhere across the universe. Finding themselves in a strange new environment with strange new creatures, they meet a dinosaur named Mo - and that's just the beginning of their out of this world adventure!

title: To Balderly Go
description: Prohyas is crushed when his good hair day becomes a no hair day and Vambre has to battle a furry monster alone while her bro is in shock without his locks!

title: Bao Bao's Revenge
description: When Mao Mao's old partner threatens the kingdom, his friends will need to learn about his past in order to protect the present.

title: Fear of Flying
description: Uncle grandpa helps a young boy overcome his fear of flying.

title: Not Yours
description: Bing's helping Flop pick up groceries in Padget's shop today. And while Flop is paying, Bing picks up a lolly and puts it in his pocket. But what happens when Flop explains to Bing that he has stolen the lolly?

title: Drawn to Making it Happen with Sidney Keys
description: Cartoon Network celebrates Black History Month with Sidney Keys III, a 15-year-old rising entrepreneur and the founder and CEO of "Books n Bros," an African American literature book club for male youth ages 7-13 years old. Focused on promoting literacy among young Black boys and introducing them to positive representation in literature, Keys' advocacy is paving the way for change by creating a place for boys to be mentored by their "Big Bros" and connect over a shared love for reading.

title: Uh, Oh, Dynamo
description: Worried about his little girls' safety, the Professor creates Powerpuff Dynamo, a state-of-the-art protection system, to help them in battle.

title: Wednesday - Part 1
description: Elliott and his mom Frankie are about to have a Wednesday they'll never forget, when a mysterious rock unexpectedly transports them somewhere across the universe. Finding themselves in a strange new environment with strange new creatures, they meet a dinosaur named Mo - and that's just the beginning of their out of this world adventure!

title: Uncle Fashion
description: Uncle Grandpa helps a young boy who wants to be a fashion designer by taking him somewhere his style will be appreciated.

title: Drawn to Community
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating awesome kids who are giving back and making a difference to those around them. CN is recognizing extraordinary girls who are channeling their interests into outreach as they are Drawn to… Community!

title: G'day Mornin'
description: Uncle grandpa goes to Australia where he must stop an out-of-control collecting kangaroo before he destroys the Earth.

title: Nueva Mascota
description: Después de que Chata les dijera que no pueden tener una mascota, Vic y Val adoptan un lagarto salvaje, sin conocer sus propiedades mágicas, y deciden mantenerlo en secreto para que Chata no se entere.

title: That's the Way the Windmill Blows!/Mecha Machine Makers!
description: The windmill isn't turning, which means Sunny Field Farm has no power. The windmill needs to turn again so Zee can launch his rocket!/Izzy and Timmy are making a bird caller for Grandma, but have trouble connecting pieces of their machine.

title: Ghost Train
description: Percy has to deliver the mail on Halloween when everyone knows the legendary Ghost Train comes out! Thomas rolls along to help Percy face his fears, but when a "real" Ghost Train appears... things get almost spooky.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Una Nueva Vida
description: Manzana y Cebollín abandonan sus hogares y se mudan a la ciudad, donde se conocen por primera vez.
